emuInput.TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Home Makers Guild members, from left, seated: Sarah Morse; front row: Leona Edwards, Ethel Jackson, Florence Burrell, Rev. C. A. Burell, Sadye Wilborn, Edith Johnson, and Edan Jones; rear: Maggie Blackwell, Violet Johnson, Zula Thomas, and Edna Avery, posed in Mt. Ararat Baptist Church, another version
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 24, 1962, pg. 27 reads: "Home Makers Guild - The Home Makers Guild will present an all-star program at Mt. Ararat Baptist Church, March 2, at 8 P.M. Seated: Mrs. Sarah Morse, president.  Left to right, front row: Mmes. Leona Edwards, Ethel Jackson, Florence Burrell, the Rev. C. A. Burell, Mmes. Sadye Wilborn, Edith Johnson and Edan Jones.  Rear: Mmes. Maggie Blackwell, Violet Johnson, Zula Thomas and Edna Avery. - Harris Photo."
